    {
      "bookmarkId": "681638_27_1758-1773",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "1758-1773",
      "markText": "事实上，他可以成为完美的妻子。",
      "totalCount": 957,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=681638&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=1758&rangeEnd=1773",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1a6326005a66a61a69a7ad9?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=1758&rangeEnd=1773"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "681638_8_5066-5106",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5066-5106",
      "markText": "在1932年到1933年那场人为的饥荒中，整个乌克兰有七百万到一千万的人被饿死。",
      "totalCount": 918,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=681638&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5066&rangeEnd=5106",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1a6326005a66a61a69a7ad9?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5066&rangeEnd=5106"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "681638_18_1095-1152",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1095-1152",
      "markText": "舒拉姨妈说：“拿一只苹果，往里面戳入铁钉，放一晚上，然后拔出钉子，吃掉苹果——这样一来你就能摄取到维生素C和铁。”",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=681638&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1095&rangeEnd=1152",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1a6326005a66a61a69a7ad9?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1095&rangeEnd=1152"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "681638_8_6556-6618",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6556-6618",
      "markText": "婚礼，如同葬礼一样，为家庭戏剧提供了完美的表演场所：有各种各样的仪式和象征性习俗，并为趋炎附势提供了乔装打扮纷纷亮相的机会。",
      "totalCount": 846,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=681638&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6556&rangeEnd=6618",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1a6326005a66a61a69a7ad9?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6556&rangeEnd=6618"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "681638_3_9368-9406",
      "chapterUid": 3,
